26th January, 2006

When using the persistant death system when a player logs in, after a server reset, his death corpse will appear at the GraveYard marker.
It's recommeneded you place the GraveYard marker in a temple along with the BagYard marker.

The GodLoc Marker is used if the God System is in use.
If the player has a valid deity and are saved at the time of death they will appear at the GodLoc marker.
It's recommended you place this in your temple also.
The default chance that a player will be raised by their god if they have one by  is 5% +1% per 4 levels of the character.
The marble is smooth and cool to the touch. You find it hard to determine where the stone ends and the water begins.
